edia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991825689, \"rank\": 8.174200612277874e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 16-year-old is set to have surgery when she returns home after the Games, but for now will rely on heavy strapping to minimise the pain.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky Brown will compete in the women's park skateboarding heats, which are scheduled to start at 11:30am BST on Tuesday, August 6.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0923154974689657e-13, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown is set to go in heat four.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will hope to book her place in the final, which will take place at 4:30pm later in the day.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TV channel:In the UK, the women's park will be shown on BBC and Eurosport.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997215650655918, \"rank\": 0.00027850567754042477, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.or